re the entire sun is blocked by the moon’s shadow. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.theguardian.com/cities/2017/aug/21/portland-oregon-spotlight-great-american-eclipse"&gt;Continue reading...&lt;/a&gt;</description> <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/cities/cities">Cities</category> <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/portland">Portland</category> <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/us-news">US news</category> <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/world/world">World news</category> <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/science/solar-eclipse">Solar eclipses</category> <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/science/science">Science</category> <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/science/space">Space</category> <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/culture/culture">Culture</category> <pubDate>Mon, 21 Aug 2017 11:37:46 GMT</pubDate> <guid>https://www.theguardian.com/cities/2017/aug/21/portland-oregon-spotlight-great-american-eclipse</guid> <media:content width="140" url="https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/86e4f910a211b452bd6fe2eaad854d963b323cf8/0_406_6016_3610/master/6016.jpg?w=140&amp;q=55&amp;auto=format&amp;usm=12&amp;fit=max&amp;s=ed87c9cf086925ea45416c5bd3b19362"> <media:credit scheme="urn:ebu">Photograph: Alamy Stock Photo</media:credit> </media:content> <media:content width="460" url="https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/86e4f910a211b452bd6fe2eaad854d963b323cf8/0_406_6016_3610/master/6016.jpg?w=460&amp;q=55&amp;auto=format&amp;usm=12&amp;fit=max&amp;s=f9684034b4f3c465712c5d125139a026"> <media:credit scheme="urn:ebu">Photograph: Alamy Stock Photo</media:credit> </media:content> <dc:creator>Lauren Dake in Portland</dc:creator> <dc:date>2017-08-21T11:37:46Z</dc:date> </item> <item> <title>Arizona's 'concentration camp': why was Tent City kept open for 24 years?</title> <link>https://www.theguardian.com/cities/2017/aug/21/arizona-phoenix-concentration-camp-tent-city-jail-joe-arpaio-immigr